title: Ep. 2779 - Bagha And Natu Kaka Reunite - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 22 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal sees humility in both Bagha and Natu kaka and the way they actually respect each other. He lets them realize that both have no reason to quarrel now. Hence, they reunite. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2780 - Unmindful Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 23 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal unmindfully collides with Champaklal in the house and apologizes. Later, in the society, he again unmindfully sings a song and is just about to collide with a car. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2781 - Problem In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 24 July 2019
shortDesc: A problem arises in Gokuldham, a goods truck driver enters society and creates a problem for the members. Later as Jethalal tries to shut the problem by talking to him, he rather threatens Jethalal and goes away. What will happen next? Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2782 - Argument With Tempo Drivers - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 25 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal is scared because of some Tempo drivers. Chachaji gets kidnapped by a group of people. Jethalal is at work improving his mood. All others are looking for clues to find Chachaji. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2783 - Sodhi Is Angry - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 26 July 2019
shortDesc: Society members are worried because the Gada family is nowhere to be found and they are unable to reach Natu Kaka and Bagha as well. When Sodhi gets to know that Champaklal is kidnapped he gets angry.

title: Ep. 2784 - Chaos At The Police Station - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 29 July 2019
shortDesc: Champaklal is kidnapped and the men from Gokuldham go to the police station to file a complaint. Everyone is anxious about the proceedings of the case and create chaos at the police station. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2785 - Tempo Driver Comes Clean - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 30 July 2019
shortDesc: The Tempo driver comes to the police station. He tells everything that he knew and swears that it wasn't him who kidnapped the old man. Everyone is shocked and Inspector Chalu Pandey is in confusion. How will they solve the case?

title: Ep. 2786 - Way To Find The KIdnappers - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 31 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal, Chalu Pandey and the others are looking for a way to find the kidnappers. They have no clue but then, together these men come up with an idea to find the car and through it, the kidnappers. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2787 - Confirmation From Checkpost - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 1 August 2019
shortDesc: Chalu Pandey and Jethalal check CCTV footage and learns that the car has left Mumbai. At least now they have a direction to look forward to. This will help them find Champak Chacha. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2788 - Obstacles On The Way - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 2 August 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal and Chalu Pandey have their car wrecked and they take a lift in a dung truck. The others also adjust and sacrifice just find Champak Chacha. Inspector Pandey and gang reach the location. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2789 - Finding Champak Chacha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 5 August 2019
shortDesc: The Gokuldham Society reaches the resort as per the location. They decide to split up and check-in each room of the resort. Jethalal and Iyer act as housekeeping guys and check a few of the rooms. But still, are unable to find Champak Chacha.

title: Ep. 2790 - Champak Chacha Is Found - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 6 August 2019
shortDesc: Everyone gathers around the water park and there is still no word about Champak Chacha. They wait for Chalu Pandey's report, but even he was unable to find Champak Chacha. Upset about the fact Tappu and Jethalal start crying.

title: Ep. 2791 - Tappu Sena Play Cricket - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 7 August 2019
shortDesc: Tappu Sena decides to play cricket in Gokuldham Society. Tappu goes for first batting, and everyone asks him to hit the ball gently. Seeing the kids play Abdul also decides to join them. Stay Tuned, for a fun day at Gokuldham Society.

title: Ep. 2792 - Bhide Loses It - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 8 August 2019
shortDesc: Bhide asks Tappu Sena to make less noise around society. But they were playing cricket and it gets too loud for Bhide. He wants to have a quiet time and wants to enjoy his food. But how can he, when he is busy scolding Tappu for playing cricket.

title: Ep. 2793 - Madhvi Knows It All - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 9 August 2019
shortDesc: Bhide takes the cricket kit back to his house. Madhvi is trying to fix the issue but Bhide is not ready to listen. Suddenly he gets the news that Sonu is in Ratnagiri and they decided to visit her.
